      Static method to obtain an instance of the builder of Options.

      Options.Builder Options.Builder.setEventPostProcessor​(EventPostProcessor eventPostProcessor)

      Options.Builder Options.Builder.setGlobalDynamicFields​(Map<String,? extends ValueSupplier<?>> globalDynamicFields)
      Set this to supply fields to events, where keys are fixed but values are dynamically created at runtime.
      Options.Builder Options.Builder.setGlobalFields​(Map<String,?> globalFields)
      Set this to supply fields to all events, where both keys and values are fixed.

      SampleRate is the rate at which to sample this event.

      WriteKey is the Honeycomb authentication token.
